T02TD1268E:28b-1: shr'i he badzra ratna pra lo ke s'a dha nam n'a ma /
T02TD1268E:28b-3: dpal dgyes pa rdo rje'i sgrub thabs rin po che'i sgron ma zhes bya ba /
T02TD1268E:28b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1268E:28b-5: he ru ka dang bdag med bcas //
T02TD1268E:28b-7: de 'dod phyir na de sgrub thabs //
T02TD1268E:28b-8: de don gnyer la sgron 'di bri //
T02TD1268E:28b-9: chags med byang chub sems dang ldan //
T02TD1268E:28b-10: dbang thob blo ldan lung blangs pas //
T02TD1268E:28b-11: dur khrod la sogs gnas bde bar //
T02TD1268E:28b-12: rnal 'byor brtson pas bsgrub par bya'o //
T02TD1268E:28b-13: tho rangs byams pas mal nas langs //
T02TD1268E:28b-14: gdong la sogs pa dis bkrus nas //
T02TD1268E:28b-15: rdo rjes mtshan pa'i stan la 'dug / bdud rtsi'i ri lu lce la gzhag / snying rjes ma rnams gzung byas la //
T02TD1268E:28b-16: zhal brgyad nga rgyal bdag bsgoms te //
T02TD1268E:28b-17: rakshas sa sbyang gnas bsrung ba //
T02TD1268E:28b-18: me ri dra gur brtan par bsgom //
T02TD1268E:28b-19: he ru ka yi snying ga ru //
T02TD1268E:28b-20: bam dang ram las gsal bar ni //
T02TD1268E:28b-21: padma nyi ma dmar po bsgom //
T02TD1268E:28b-22: de steng h'um nag 'od zer lngas //
T02TD1268E:29a-0: @29a * // phyogs bcur spros pa bskul dang sbyang //
T02TD1268E:29a-1: byas nas thams cad mkha' la bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:29a-2: bla ma sangs rgyas rang dag lha //
T02TD1268E:29a-3: gsal bsgoms lus sprul phyag bya'o //
T02TD1268E:29a-4: de yang 'og nas ston pa yi //
T02TD1268E:29a-5: bcom ldan sku mdog phyag dang rgyan //
T02TD1268E:29a-6: phyag mtshan bcas pa bzhugs pa ni //
T02TD1268E:29a-7: bdag med yum dang ldan pa'o //
T02TD1268E:29a-8: de mdun goo r'i nag mo ni //
T02TD1268E:29a-9: byang chub sems dkar ri bong can //
T02TD1268E:29a-10: g-yas na tsoo r'i dmar mo yang //
T02TD1268E:29a-12: rgyab na ser mo be t'a l'i //
T02TD1268E:29a-13: lhung bzed chu bzang bkang ba 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-14: g-yon na ljang gu ghasma r'i //
T02TD1268E:29a-15: dri bzang thod pa bkang pa 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-16: byang shar pukka s'i sngon mo //
T02TD1268E:29a-17: sha lngas thod pa bkang ba 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-18: me na mdog dkar sha ba r'i //
T02TD1268E:29a-19: ro ldan btung ba sna tshogs 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-21: da ma ru sgrog sgra rnams 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-22: rlung na do mb'i sna tshogs gzugs //
T02TD1268E:29a-23: phyag rgya bsnol nas mchod pa 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-24: bla ma mi bskyod spyi bor bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:29a-25: gsal bar brtan par legs bsgoms la //
T02TD1268E:29a-26: snying ga'i sa bon spro bsdu las //
T02TD1268E:29a-27: phyi yi lha mo mchod pa'i tshogs //
T02TD1268E:29a-28: yon chab me tog spos la sogs //
T02TD1268E:29a-29: rab gnas le'u'i snags kyis mchod //
T02TD1268E:29a-30: sa bon spros la goo r'i'i tshogs //
T02TD1268E:29a-31: bshams dang gnas nas byon pa dang //
T02TD1268E:29a-32: mdun na gnas pa'i rim pa yis //
T02TD1268E:29a-33: bdud rtsi lnga dang sha lnga 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-34: gtso bo'i sa bon gyis bskul nas //
T02TD1268E:29a-35: dom b'i gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul //
T02TD1268E:29a-36: mchod pa'i lha mo thams cad kyang //
T02TD1268E:29a-37: spros pa de dag gnas nas bsdu //
T02TD1268E:29a-38: de nas de dag mdun du yang //
T02TD1268E:29a-39: pus btsugs thal sbyar 'jigs sems kyis //
T02TD1268E:29a-40: thog med dus nas deng dus su //
T02TD1268E:29a-41: 'khor bas 'khor bar bsags pa'i sdig / bgyis dang bgyid du stsal ba dang //
T02TD1268E:29a-42: yi rang bshags shing slan chad bsdam //
T02TD1268E:29a-43: sangs rgyas byang chub sems dpa' dang //
T02TD1268E:29a-44: rang rgyal nyan thos so so yi //
T02TD1268E:29a-45: skye bo'i dge la rjes yi rang //
T02TD1268E:29a-46: gsum la skyabs dang sems gnyis bskyed //
T02TD1268E:29a-47: bskul dang gsol bdag kyang gdab //
T02TD1268E:29a-48: thams cad byang chub chen por bsdo //
T02TD1268E:29b-0: de nas byams @29b dang snying rje dang //
T02TD1268E:29b-1: dga' dang btang snyoms yun rings bsgom //
T02TD1268E:29b-2: de nyid gsum dang mu: brjod pas //
T02TD1268E:29b-3: mdun gyi spyan drangs gnas su gshegs //
T02TD1268E:29b-4: chos rnams stong par shes byas la //
T02TD1268E:29b-5: blo gnas pa la sngags 'di brjod //
T02TD1268E:29b-6: aom sva bh'a ba shuddha: sarba dharm'a sva bh'a ba shuddho& ham //
T02TD1268E:29b-7: brjod pas gzung ba'i chos rnams kun //
T02TD1268E:29b-8: rmi lam mig 'phrul smig rgyu dang //
T02TD1268E:29b-9: chu zla mig yor sgyu ma tsam //
T02TD1268E:29b-10: sems snang tsam las yod ma yin //
T02TD1268E:29b-11: aom sh'u n+ya t'a dzny'a na badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1268E:29b-12: brjod pas sems snang de dag kun //
T02TD1268E:29b-13: rdul dang du ba khug rna sprin //
T02TD1268E:29b-14: skyon bral ston ka'i nyi phyed kyi //
T02TD1268E:29b-15: nam mkha'i dkyil ltar sems gzhag bya //
T02TD1268E:29b-16: chos nyid spros dang bral ba las //
T02TD1268E:29b-17: smon lam byams pas 'gro ba dran //
T02TD1268E:29b-18: nam mkha'i dkyil du ram dang h'um //
T02TD1268E:29b-20: de nas h'um las byung ba yi //
T02TD1268E:29b-21: sna tshogs rdo rje'i sa gzhi dang //
T02TD1268E:29b-22: ra ba gur dang bla re dang //
T02TD1268E:29b-24: de nas ae las chos kyi dbyings //
T02TD1268E:29b-25: chos 'byung gru gsum nam mkha' mnyam //
T02TD1268E:29b-26: bsgoms pa'i nang du yam ram bam //
T02TD1268E:29b-27: lam bzhi sngo dmar dkar dang ser //
T02TD1268E:29b-28: yam zhu sngon po gzhu yi dbyibs //
T02TD1268E:29b-29: rlung gi dkyil 'khor ba dan ldan //
T02TD1268E:29b-30: de steng ram las gru gsum dmar //
T02TD1268E:29b-31: me yi dkyil 'khor ram gyis mtshan //
T02TD1268E:29b-32: de steng bam las zlum po dkar //
T02TD1268E:29b-33: chu yi dkyil 'khor bum pas mtshan //
T02TD1268E:29b-34: de steng lam las grub bzhi ser //
T02TD1268E:29b-35: sa yi dkyil 'khor rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1268E:29b-36: sems kyi snang bas de rnams zhu //
T02TD1268E:29b-37: snang ba mched pas gzhal yas grub //
T02TD1268E:29b-38: rin po che las grub pa yi //
T02TD1268E:29b-39: zur bzhi sgo bzhi logs bzhi pa //
T02TD1268E:29b-40: rta babs bzhi dang ka ba brgyad //
T02TD1268E:29b-41: mchod pa sna tshogs rgyan gyis mdzes //
T02TD1268E:29b-42: chos kyi 'khor lo ri dgas gdugs //
T02TD1268E:29b-43: ba dan dril bu 'phan la sogs //
T02TD1268E:29b-44: sangs rgyas mang po'i snang bas khyab //
T02TD1268E:29b-45: dra ba dra phyed tva ra na //
T02TD1268E:29b-46: bum pa rdo rje phreng ba dang //
T02TD1268E:29b-47: sgo khyud zla phyed rdo rje mdzes //
T02TD1268E:29b-48: dur khrod brgyad na mtsho brgyad klu //
T02TD1268E:29b-49: shing brgyad zhing skyong gdan mgo brgyad //
T02TD1268E:29b-50: phyogs skyong chung ma bu 'khor brgyad //
T02TD1268E:29b-51: steng na lha brgyad lha yi 'khor //
T02TD1268E:29b-52: mchod rten brgyad dang rnal 'byor tshogs //
T02TD1268E:30a-1: bya dang gcan gzan sna tshogs sprul //
T02TD1268E:30a-2: sha za gdug pa ro yi tshogs //
T02TD1268E:30a-3: shar sogs sgo yi logs rim par //
T02TD1268E:30a-4: glu ma gar ma yon chab ma //
T02TD1268E:30a-5: me tog spos dang mar me ma //
T02TD1268E:30a-6: dri chab zhal zas sgra sna tshogs //
T02TD1268E:30a-7: gzugs sgra dri ro reg bya chos //
T02TD1268E:30a-8: rgyan phreng ma rnams sna tshogs mdog / de nang dkar ser dmar dang ljang //
T02TD1268E:30a-9: gzhal yas dbus ni mthing ga 'bar //
T02TD1268E:30a-10: rdo rje ra ba padmar ldan //
T02TD1268E:30a-11: ge sar bdud bzhi nyi mas mnan //
T02TD1268E:30a-12: pad ma brgyad la lha brgyad bri //
T02TD1268E:30a-13: snying gar zla bas mnan pa'o //
T02TD1268E:30a-14: mdzes pa'i gzhal yas de nang gi / dbus kyi bdud bzhi'i nyi steng du //
T02TD1268E:30a-15: h'um dang aam las 'og dang steng //
T02TD1268E:30a-18: thod pa gri gug phyag mtshan ma //
T02TD1268E:30a-19: sa bon gnas pa spro bsdus pas //
T02TD1268E:30a-20: thams cad gcig tu gyur pa las //
T02TD1268E:30a-21: zhal brgyad yum dang kha sbyar ba //
T02TD1268E:30a-22: 'og gzhi gsal bar bsgom par bya //
T02TD1268E:30a-23: chags can bskyab phyir thugs rje yis //
T02TD1268E:30a-24: bdag nyid thugs ka'i sa bon las //
T02TD1268E:30a-25: phyogs bcur sangs rgyas gtsug tu byon //
T02TD1268E:30a-26: thugs kar sa bon so sor gnas //
T02TD1268E:30a-27: aom padma su kham dha ra ma h'a r'a ga datta tsa tur a'a nanda bha ga bi shva h'um h'um h'um ka r+yam ku ru shva me /
T02TD1268E:30a-28: padma sngags kyis byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1268E:30a-29: de nas rdo rje byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1268E:30a-30: aom badzra ma h'a dve sha tsa tur a'a nanda d'a ya ka kha ga mu kha ae ka ra so n'a tha h'um h'um h'um ka r+yam ku ru shva me /
T02TD1268E:30a-31: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta aa nu r'a ga ta badzra sva bh'a ba a'a tma ko& ham /
T02TD1268E:30a-32: de ni sbyor ba dang po yin //
T02TD1268E:30a-33: de nas rjes su chags pa yis //
T02TD1268E:30a-34: shar sogs tshangs sogs snying ga ru //
T02TD1268E:30a-35: gam tsam bam gham pam sham lam dam //
T02TD1268E:30a-36: de nas phyogs mtshams rnams su babs //
T02TD1268E:30a-37: shar du gam yig gsal ba las //
T02TD1268E:30a-38: a'a li nyis 'gyur las zla ba'i //
T02TD1268E:30a-39: dkyil 'khor me long ye shes dang //
T02TD1268E:30a-40: steng du k'a li nyis 'gyur las //
T02TD1268E:30a-41: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor mnyam pa nyid //
T02TD1268E:30a-42: gam gyur gri gug nag po la //
T02TD1268E:30a-43: zla ba sa bon so sor rtog / sa bon sprul sbyang gcig gyur pa //
T02TD1268E:30a-44: bya ba nan tan ye shes yin //
T02TD1268E:30a-45: goo r'i bzhengs pa'i sku de ni //
T02TD1268E:30a-46: chos kyi dbyings kyi ye shes so //
T02TD1268E:30b-0: sngon du @30b bsgoms pa'i gtso bo dang //
T02TD1268E:30b-1: 'og gi lha mo bdun po yang //
T02TD1268E:30b-2: de bzhin ye shes lnga yi sku //
T02TD1268E:30b-3: rnal 'byor pa yis brtan par bsgom //
T02TD1268E:30b-4: shar du gri gug las byung ba'i //
T02TD1268E:30b-5: tshangs pa'i steng na goo r'i nag / g-yas na gri gug g-yon na nya //
T02TD1268E:30b-6: gzugs kyi phung po rang bzhin bsgom //
T02TD1268E:30b-7: lho ru dbang po'i steng gnas dmar //
T02TD1268E:30b-8: da ma ru las tsoo r'i bzhengs //
T02TD1268E:30b-9: da ma ru g-yas phag pa g-yon //
T02TD1268E:30b-10: tshor ba'i phung po'i rang bzhin bsgom //
T02TD1268E:30b-11: nub tu bam las be t'a l'i //
T02TD1268E:30b-12: gser mdog nye dbang gdan la bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:30b-13: g-yas na rus sbal thod pa g-yon //
T02TD1268E:30b-14: 'du shes phung po'i rang bzhin bsgom //
T02TD1268E:30b-15: byang du gham las ghasma r'i //
T02TD1268E:30b-16: drag po'i steng na mar kata mdog / sprul g-yas phyag g-yon thod pa 'dzin //
T02TD1268E:30b-17: 'du byed phung po'i rang bzhin bsgom //
T02TD1268E:30b-18: byang shar pam las seng ge las //
T02TD1268E:30b-19: pukka s'i sngo gshin rje'i steng //
T02TD1268E:30b-20: g-yas na seng ge dgra sta g-yon //
T02TD1268E:30b-21: sa yi khams kyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD1268E:30b-22: me ru sham dang dge slong las //
T02TD1268E:30b-23: sha ba r'i dkar gnod sbyin gdan //
T02TD1268E:30b-24: g-yas na dge slong gsil byed g-yon //
T02TD1268E:30b-25: chu yi khams kyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD1268E:30b-26: srin por lam dang 'khor lo las //
T02TD1268E:30b-27: gtum mo mkha' mdog srin po mnan //
T02TD1268E:30b-28: g-yas na 'khor lo thong gshol g-yon //
T02TD1268E:30b-29: me yi khams kyi rang bzhin no //
T02TD1268E:30b-30: rlung du dam dang rdo rje las //
T02TD1268E:30b-31: dam b'i kha dog sna tshogs te //
T02TD1268E:30b-32: rdo rje g-yas la sdigs mdzub g-yon //
T02TD1268E:30b-33: rlung gi khams kyi rang bzhin bsgo ma //
T02TD1268E:30b-34: lha mo de rnams spyan gsum ma //
T02TD1268E:30b-35: dmar zhing zlum la mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1268E:30b-36: dbu skra kham ser gyen du mdzes //
T02TD1268E:30b-37: rus thod 'khor lo snyan cha dang //
T02TD1268E:30b-38: mgul rgyan la sogs phyag rgya lnga //
T02TD1268E:30b-39: mi mgo skam po bco lnga'i phreng //
T02TD1268E:30b-40: gcer bu g-yon brkyang gar thabs bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:30b-41: gtso la 'dud pa'i stangs dang ldan //
T02TD1268E:30b-42: bar dor gnas pa'i lus ngag yid //
T02TD1268E:30b-43: aom dang a'a: h'um dkar dmar nag / ho: gnyis thabs dang shes rab brten //
T02TD1268E:30b-44: 'khor los sgyu ma ltar mthong nas //
T02TD1268E:30b-45: gtso bo'i spyir zhugs gtso nyid zhu //
T02TD1268E:30b-46: yum yang zhu nas h'um aam gnyis //
T02TD1268E:30b-47: sa bon dkyil 'khor dbus gnas pa //
T02TD1268E:30b-48: rtog med bde ba chen por bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:31a-2: shin tu 'dod pa'i sems gdungs pas //
T02TD1268E:31a-3: pukka s'i sogs lha mo bzhis //
T02TD1268E:31a-4: rdo rje'i glu ni len par byed //
T02TD1268E:31a-5: rje btsun thugs rje'i yid bzhengs shig / pukka s'i ni bdag la skyobs //
T02TD1268E:31a-6: stong pa'i rang bzhin nyid spongs la //
T02TD1268E:31a-7: bdag la bde chen sbyor ba mdzod //
T02TD1268E:31a-8: khyod mi bzhugs na bdag 'gum pas //
T02TD1268E:31a-9: thugs rje rgyun chad ma mdzad bzhengs //
T02TD1268E:31a-10: stong nyid bcom ldan ci la bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:31a-12: dga' gtso 'jig rten mgron pos nas //
T02TD1268E:31a-13: stong pa nyid la bzhugs sa ma ci //
T02TD1268E:31a-14: gtum mo bdag ni gsol 'debs na //
T02TD1268E:31a-15: bcom ldan kye yi rdo rje bzhengs //
T02TD1268E:31a-16: bdag gis khyod kyi thugs 'tshal gyis //
T02TD1268E:31a-18: shig /dom b'i bdag ni dran nyams pas //
T02TD1268E:31a-19: bcom ldan dgyes pa rdo rje bzhengs //
T02TD1268E:31a-20: rdo rje glu ni sgra snyan gyis //
T02TD1268E:31a-21: rmi lam lta bur gtso bo bzhengs //
T02TD1268E:31a-22: mngon byang lnga yi ye shes las //
T02TD1268E:31a-23: bcom ldan dgyes pa rdo rje nyid //
T02TD1268E:31a-24: dkyil 'khor dbus na gar dgur bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:31a-25: zhal brgyad pa la phyag bcu drug / steng zhal dud mdog mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1268E:31a-26: kham ser skra brje sa 'khor lo rus //
T02TD1268E:31a-27: sna tshogs rdo rjes dbu skra brgyan //
T02TD1268E:31a-28: dang po sku dang mthun pa'i zhal //
T02TD1268E:31a-29: g-yas dkar g-yas gnyis sku dang mthun //
T02TD1268E:31a-30: g-yon dmar g-yon gnyis ji bzhin sku //
T02TD1268E:31a-31: dbu skra gyen 'bar thod lnga'i thod //
T02TD1268E:31a-32: spyan gsum dmar zlum mche ba gtsigs //
T02TD1268E:31a-33: snyan cha 'gul rgyan dpung ba'i rgyan //
T02TD1268E:31a-34: phyag zhabs gdu bu 'og pag rgyan /
T02TD1268E:31a-35: stag gi sham thabs steng na bcings //
T02TD1268E:31a-36: thong rlon phreng ba thal bas phyugs //
T02TD1268E:31a-37: tshangs pa brgya byin nye dbang drag / steng na zhabs bzhi g-yas brkyang bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:31a-38: phyag g-yas dang po glang po che //
T02TD1268E:31a-39: thod par gnas pas yum la 'khyud //
T02TD1268E:31a-40: de bzhin rta bod glang rnga mo //
T02TD1268E:31a-41: mi dang seng ge byi la bsnams //
T02TD1268E:31a-42: phyag g-yas thod pa'i rim par 'dzin //
T02TD1268E:31a-43: phyag g-yon dang po thod pa'i nang //
T02TD1268E:31a-44: sa yi lha mo bcas pa 'khyud //
T02TD1268E:31a-45: steng 'og rim par thod par gnas //
T02TD1268E:31a-46: chu dang me dang rlung nyi ma //
T02TD1268E:31a-47: zla ba gshin rje nor sbyin no //
T02TD1268E:31a-48: de yum zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
T02TD1268E:31b-0: mdog @31b nag gri gug thod pas 'khyud //
T02TD1268E:31b-1: phyag rgya lngas brgyan thod skam phreng //
T02TD1268E:31b-2: skra ser gyen 'bar spyan gsum dmar //
T02TD1268E:31b-3: bdag po ro myang g-yon brkyang zhabs //
T02TD1268E:31b-4: bdud bzhi'i steng na mnyam par bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:31b-5: de nas bdag dang 'khor de dag / gsal bar legs par brtan par bsgom //
T02TD1268E:31b-6: bde gsal dkyil 'khor rgyal po mchog / ting 'dzin gsum du bstan pa yin //
T02TD1268E:31b-7: de dag gsal ni rang rang gi / snying gar gdan la phyag mtshan bsgom //
T02TD1268E:31b-8: de yi sa bon phyogs bcur spro //
T02TD1268E:31b-9: bskul sbyangs sa bon so sor thim //
T02TD1268E:31b-10: h'um gis ye shes 'khor lo bkug / shar gyi nam mkhar bzhugs la mchod //
T02TD1268E:31b-11: dza: h'um bam ho: lha mo bzhis //
T02TD1268E:31b-12: dgug gzhug gnyis med dgyes par bya //
T02TD1268E:31b-13: de nas skye mched byin gyis brlab //
T02TD1268E:31b-14: gtso bo 'khor lo thams cad kyi //
T02TD1268E:31b-15: mig la gti mug rdo rje dkar //
T02TD1268E:31b-16: rna bar zhe sdang rdo rje nag / sna la ser sna rdo rje ser //
T02TD1268E:31b-17: lce la 'dod chags rdo rje dmar //
T02TD1268E:31b-18: lus la phrag dog rdo rje ljang //
T02TD1268E:31b-19: yid la bdag med rnal 'byor gnag / de dag tshangs sogs pad zla'i steng //
T02TD1268E:31b-20: gri gug thod pa phyag rgya lnga //
T02TD1268E:31b-21: sku gsung thugs kyang byin brlabs te //
T02TD1268E:31b-22: mgo dang kha dang snying ga ru //
T02TD1268E:31b-23: aom dang a'a: h'um dkar dmar nag / sa spyod mkha' spyod bdag med ma //
T02TD1268E:31b-24: gri gug thod pa 'dzin pa yi //
T02TD1268E:31b-25: pad zla tshangs pa dag la bsgom //
T02TD1268E:31b-26: yang ni rang snying sa bon gyis //
T02TD1268E:31b-27: phyogs bcu'i bla ma rgyal ba dang //
T02TD1268E:31b-28: 'khor lo khro bo lha mo rnams //
T02TD1268E:31b-29: spyan drangs mchod nas gsol ba 'debs //
T02TD1268E:31b-30: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta aa bhi shinytsa tu m'am //
T02TD1268E:31b-31: brjod pas gnang nas rigs lnga yis //
T02TD1268E:31b-32: bum pa bdud rtsis bkang pas bskur //
T02TD1268E:31b-33: rigs kyi bdag pos spyi bor mtshan //
T02TD1268E:31b-34: bdag la mi bskyod rdo rje yis //
T02TD1268E:31b-35: phyogs kyi lha mo bzhi po la //
T02TD1268E:31b-36: mi bskyod rnam snang rin chen 'byung //
T02TD1268E:31b-37: 'od dpag med dang bzhi yang bsgom //
T02TD1268E:31b-38: de bzhin zhe sdang gti mug dang //
T02TD1268E:31b-39: ser sna 'dod chags bzhi yis kyang //
T02TD1268E:31b-40: pukka s'i sogs mtshams bzhi la //
T02TD1268E:31b-41: rim pas spyi bor mchan par bsgom //
T02TD1268E:31b-42: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta aa bhi she ka badzra sva bh'a wa a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1268E:31b-43: da ni bdud rtsi myang bar bya //
T02TD1268E:31b-44: yam ram a'a: h'um aom rnams bsgom //
T02TD1268E:32a-2: rlung dang me dang thod sgyed dang //
T02TD1268E:32a-3: sa bon gnas pa'i ka p'a la //
T02TD1268E:32a-4: h'um gis sbyangs dang a'a: yis 'bar //
T02TD1268E:32a-5: aom gyis ye shes bdud rtsir 'bab //
T02TD1268E:32a-6: bhr'um dzr'im a'am kham h'um lnga dang //
T02TD1268E:32a-7: nam ham sham sham gham dang lnga //
T02TD1268E:32a-8: bdud rtsir gyur pa rdo rje lces //
T02TD1268E:32a-9: myangs la 'khor lo bde bas mchod //
T02TD1268E:32a-10: de la sngags 'dis brtan par bya'o //
T02TD1268E:32a-11: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta aa mri ta sva da badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham //
T02TD1268E:32a-12: h'um gis sa bon gyis bkug nas //
T02TD1268E:32a-13: sangs rgyas thams cad zhal du zhugs //
T02TD1268E:32a-14: phyir spros mchod pa'i lha mo yis //
T02TD1268E:32a-15: rim pas mchod nas gnas su thim //
T02TD1268E:32a-16: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta p'u dz'a badzra sva bh'a ba a'tma ko& ham //
T02TD1268E:32a-17: lha mo de dag rigs yum dang //
T02TD1268E:32a-18: gsung gcig tu ni mthun par bstod //
T02TD1268E:32a-19: bcom ldan lha mo brgyad kyis bskor //
T02TD1268E:32a-20: thugs rje thugs kyis 'gro ba sgrol //
T02TD1268E:32a-21: snod dang 'gro ba bcom ldan thugs //
T02TD1268E:32a-22: thugs dgyes mdzod cig bcom ldan khyod //
T02TD1268E:32a-23: phung po khams dang skye mched dang //
T02TD1268E:32a-24: dug lnga dag mdzad khyod la bstod //
T02TD1268E:32a-25: aom sarba ta th'a ga ta stu ti badzra sva bh'a ba a'atma ko& ham /
T02TD1268E:32a-26: de dag brtan par rab gsal bar //
T02TD1268E:32a-28: pho brang rnam dag rnam snang mdzad //
T02TD1268E:32a-29: rjes su chags pa rdo rje sems //
T02TD1268E:32a-30: dbang ni mi bskyod rdo rje dag / bdud rtsi myang ba 'od dpag med //
T02TD1268E:32a-31: mchod pa don yod grub pa ste //
T02TD1268E:32a-32: bstod pa rin chen 'byung ldan yin //
T02TD1268E:32a-33: yan lag drug dang ldan bsgoms pas //
T02TD1268E:32a-35: dang po sprin bar nyi ma 'dra //
T02TD1268E:32a-36: gnyis pa sgyu ma lta bur snang //
T02TD1268E:32a-37: snang ba thob pa rmi lam ltar //
T02TD1268E:32a-38: 'od gsal mnyam gzhag rjes thob med //
T02TD1268E:32a-39: bdag nyid de ltar brtan gyur pas //
T02TD1268E:32a-40: 'gro ba'i sdug bsngal la bltas te //
T02TD1268E:32a-41: byams dang snying rje'i 'khor lo'i lha //
T02TD1268E:32a-42: rgyun mi chad par phyogs phyogs 'phro //
T02TD1268E:32a-43: so so'i gdul bya sbyangs byas nas //
T02TD1268E:32a-45: thabs dang shes rab las byung zhing //
T02TD1268E:32a-46: byang chub sems ni spro dang bsdu //
T02TD1268E:32a-47: mdog mtshan cha lugs thams cad kyang //
T02TD1268E:32a-48: ji ltar gsal bar brtan par bsgom //
T02TD1268E:32a-49: de ltar rdzogs bskyed rdzogs pa'i rim //
T02TD1268E:32b-0: lha mo rim par zhal la bsdu @32b zhal dang phyag rnams mtha' nas rim //
T02TD1268E:32b-1: rtsa ba'i zhal dang phyag la bsdu //
T02TD1268E:32b-2: zhabs gnyis yum la thim pa dang //
T02TD1268E:32b-3: 'khor lo bzhi yi rgya yis gdab //
T02TD1268E:32b-4: lte ba snying mgrin spyi bon //
T02TD1268E:32b-5: sprul pa chos dang longs spyod dang //
T02TD1268E:32b-6: bde ba chen po'i 'khor lo bsgom //
T02TD1268E:32b-7: de yang sku bzhi'i ngo bo yin //
T02TD1268E:32b-8: sprul par rtsa 'dab drug cu bzhi //
T02TD1268E:32b-10: k'a li bzhi dad drug cu gnas //
T02TD1268E:32b-12: snying gar rtsa 'dab brgyad gnas la //
T02TD1268E:32b-13: lte bar h'um nag 'dab ma la //
T02TD1268E:32b-14: bhr'um dzr'im a'am kham ae wam ma //
T02TD1268E:32b-15: yam dang brgyad ni legs par bsgom //
T02TD1268E:32b-16: mgrin par bcu drug 'dab ma la //
T02TD1268E:32b-18: a'a li bcu drug dag gis brgyan //
T02TD1268E:32b-19: 'bar ba'i rnam par gnas pa yin //
T02TD1268E:32b-20: spyi bor rtsa 'dab sum cu gnyis //
T02TD1268E:32b-21: lte bar ham dkar 'dab ma la //
T02TD1268E:32b-22: a'a li nyis 'gyur dag gis bskor //
T02TD1268E:32b-23: kha dog dkar po bdud rtsi 'bab //
T02TD1268E:32b-24: lta bar gtum mo sbar ba yis //
T02TD1268E:32b-25: de bzhin gshegs pa lnga bsregs shing //
T02TD1268E:32b-26: spyan la sogs pa yang bsregs te //
T02TD1268E:32b-27: bsregs pas ri bong rgyun ham 'bab //
T02TD1268E:32b-28: yi ge gsal bar gyur nas ni //
T02TD1268E:32b-29: yi ge de dag spro dang bsdu //
T02TD1268E:32b-30: bskul sbyang byas nas slar 'dus te //
T02TD1268E:32b-31: yi ge rang rang gnas la zhugs //
T02TD1268E:32b-32: srog dang rtsol ba las byung ba //
T02TD1268E:32b-35: bdud rtsi blangs nas spyi bor bsam //
T02TD1268E:32b-36: sbyangs pa'i 'khor lo rnams gang nas //
T02TD1268E:32b-37: thams cad snying gar rab tu thim //
T02TD1268E:32b-38: don dam bdud rtsi zag med bsgom //
T02TD1268E:32b-39: h'um yang rim pas n'a dar gnas //
T02TD1268E:32b-40: shin tu yun rings goms mi gnas //
T02TD1268E:32b-41: nam mkha'i dkyil ltar rngul dang bral //
T02TD1268E:32b-42: thog ma tha ma dbus med cing //
T02TD1268E:32b-44: bdag dang gzhan yang yod ma yin //
T02TD1268E:32b-45: 'di ni bde chen rgyal po yin //
T02TD1268E:32b-46: gzung dang 'dzin pa rnam par spangs //
T02TD1268E:32b-47: sems sbyong ba la skyo ngal na //
T02TD1268E:32b-48: rim pa rim par sku bskyed la //
T02TD1268E:32b-49: yab dang yum gnyis zhal phyag rgyas //
T02TD1268E:32b-50: snying gar sa bon yi ge la //
T02TD1268E:32b-51: bskor nas gnas pa zhal nas zhal //
T02TD1268E:32b-52: rdo rje lam nas padma dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-2: bsam gtan kha dog dbye ba yis //
T02TD1268E:33a-3: zhi la sogs par shes par bya //
T02TD1268E:33a-5: ping go rdho ke sha bartma ne /
T02TD1268E:33a-6: tsa tur bing sha ti ne tr'a ya /
T02TD1268E:33a-7: sho da sha bhu dz'a ya /
T02TD1268E:33a-8: kri shana dz'i m'u ta pa pu she ka p'a la m'a la aa ne kam dha ri ne /
T02TD1268E:33a-9: a'dhama ta kr'u ra tsitt'a ya /
T02TD1268E:33a-21: sapta s'a ga r'an bandha bandha /
T02TD1268E:33a-24: sarba sha tr'um sarba du shtan ha h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-30: bcom ldan 'das kyi rtsa sngags yin /
T02TD1268E:33a-31: aom de ba pi tsu badzra h'um h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-32: snying po'i sngags su shes par bya'o //
T02TD1268E:33a-33: aom badzra ka rta ri he badzr'a ya h'um h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-34: de ni nye ba'i sngags kyang yin /
T02TD1268E:33a-35: aom aa ka tsa ta ta pha ya sha h'um sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-36: grong khyer dkrug pa'i sngags yin no //
T02TD1268E:33a-37: aom tree lo ky'a ksha pa h'um h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-39: aom badzra dzr'a la dzrva la bhyo h'um h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-40: de ni phyag bzhi pa'i sngags so //
T02TD1268E:33a-41: aom ki ti ki ti badzra h'um h'um h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33a-42: phyag drug pa'i snying po yin /
T02TD1268E:33a-44: // / tshogs gnyis bsag dang gzhan dbang bsdu //
T02TD1268E:33a-45: bdag dang sems can bsrung ba'i phyir //
T02TD1268E:33a-46: lha dang chos skyong sems can la //
T02TD1268E:33a-47: bdud rtsi mchod sbyin gtor ma sbyin //
T02TD1268E:33a-48: shar lho'i dur khrod nam mkha' la //
T02TD1268E:33a-50: dbus su padma 'dab brgyad nag / shar nas phyogs mtshams go rims su //
T02TD1268E:33a-51: brgya byin gshin rje chu lha dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-52: gnod sbyin bdag po 'byung ba'i bdag / me lha srin pa rlung gi lha //
T02TD1268E:33a-53: dkar nag dmar skya ser po dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-54: dkar dmar dud ka ljang gu yi //
T02TD1268E:33a-55: mdog kyang rim pa bzhin du gsal //
T02TD1268E:33a-56: rdo rje dbyug pa sprul gyi zhags //
T02TD1268E:33a-57: dpal 'bras rtse gsum dbyu gu gsum //
T02TD1268E:33a-58: gri gug ba dan lag na thogs //
T02TD1268E:33a-59: glang po ma he chu srin dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-60: rta dang khyu mchog ra skyes dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-61: mi ro ri dags zhon pa dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-62: dur khrod rgyan dang chung ma dang //
T02TD1268E:33a-63: bu 'khor bcas pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD1268E:33a-65: shar nas rim pa snga ma ltar //
T02TD1268E:33b-0: brgya byin changs pa @33b khyab 'jug drag / gzhon nu tshogs bdag dag byed dang //
T02TD1268E:33b-1: legs ldan nag po rim par gnas //
T02TD1268E:33b-2: dkar ser dmar dang nam mkha'i mdog / dkar gnyis ser dang nag po ste //
T02TD1268E:33b-3: mdog kyang de bzhin rim par gsal //
T02TD1268E:33b-4: rdo rje dbyu gu rtse gsum dang //
T02TD1268E:33b-5: 'khor lo rtse gsum mda' gzhu dang //
T02TD1268E:33b-6: la phug ba dan ral gri 'dzin //
T02TD1268E:33b-7: padma'i gdan gnas rin chen brgyan //
T02TD1268E:33b-9: rim pa bzhin du gnas pa'o //
T02TD1268E:33b-11: sngon bzhin 'jog po dung skyong dang //
T02TD1268E:33b-12: mtha' yas rigs ldan padma che //
T02TD1268E:33b-13: dga' bo nor rgyas padma brgyad gdengs ka ka sprul zhags pad zla'i gdan //
T02TD1268E:33b-14: dkar ser dmar ljang yang dkar dang /
T02TD1268E:33b-15: sngo dang dmar skya dkar po'i mdog / rin chen rgyan dang padma dang //
T02TD1268E:33b-16: chung ma bu 'khor bcas pa dang //
T02TD1268E:33b-17: ngan 'gro gsum dang bcas pa yin //
T02TD1268E:33b-18: padma'i lte ba gsum po la //
T02TD1268E:33b-19: rang gi he ru ka nyid bsgom //
T02TD1268E:33b-20: dza: h'um bam ho: sa dgug dang gzhug / nam mkha' khyab pa'i gtso bo 'khor //
T02TD1268E:33b-21: mi ba skyod rnam snang 'od dpag med //
T02TD1268E:33b-22: rang bzhin sngo dang dkar dmar mdog / rdo rje dril bu rang 'od bcas //
T02TD1268E:33b-23: rus rgyan gtso dang 'khor de bzhin //
T02TD1268E:33b-24: de nyid gsum dang dbang bskur rgya //
T02TD1268E:33b-25: lce rnams rdo rje sbu gur bsgom //
T02TD1268E:33b-26: de rnams mdun du gtor dag la //
T02TD1268E:33b-27: byin gyis brlabs la rang bzhin btung //
T02TD1268E:33b-28: sngon du bstan pa'i bdud rtsi lnga //
T02TD1268E:33b-29: dgyes rdor lha dgur gyur pa'o //
T02TD1268E:33b-30: aom ainda dza ma dza la dzakkha bh'um ta ba hni b'a yu r'aksha tsandra s'udzdza m'a sa sa pta p'a t'a la p'a t'a la aa stha sappa sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33b-31: ai dam ba li bhu dza dzim bha pushpa dh'u pa m'am sa pingga aa mbha sarba ka dzdza khanti khu ni phe ta g'a da sv'a h'a /
T02TD1268E:33b-32: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarba dharm'a n'am /
T02TD1268E:33b-33: a'adya nu tpanna tv'a ta aom a'a: h'um phat sv'a h'a //
T02TD1268E:33b-34: gsum gsum brjod la gtor ma gtang //
T02TD1268E:33b-35: yi ge gsum dang mu: yis gshegs //
T02TD1268E:33b-36: bar chad zhi dang lhag chad zhi //
T02TD1268E:33b-37: rdo rje'i glu 'di dal bus blang //
T02TD1268E:33b-38: ko la ai ri ttha aa po l'a /
T02TD1268E:33b-40: bha ne aa kri tani dthi ha /
T02TD1268E:33b-41: ka ru ni ke a'a ai na ro la ta him ba la kha li /
T02TD1268E:33b-43: ki la ka le dzdza r'u pa ni /
T02TD1268E:33b-44: aa a'i dhu ru dhu ru /
T02TD1268E:33b-45: na dzdza aa ai tsa aa sa ma shtstsha ri si hla /
T02TD1268E:34a-1: aa ai ma khu la aa ain dha /
T02TD1268E:34a-8: aa ai ni ram su aam /
T02TD1268E:34a-10: ta aidzdza sa ra sa tsi pa ni a'a a'i ma sa sa la dzir ku ru ra b'a ta /
T02TD1268E:34a-12: ma n'a tishta badzdza aa ai /
T02TD1268E:34a-13: mchod pa dang gtor ma gtang ba //
T02TD1268E:34a-15: bza' dang btung ba longs spyod pa //
T02TD1268E:34a-16: bdud rtsi sbyor bas lus rgyas 'gyur //
T02TD1268E:34a-17: thun bzhi'i rnal 'byor ldan pa yis //
T02TD1268E:34a-18: bsgrubs na 'grub kyi gzhan du min //
T02TD1268E:34a-19: sngon du bstan pa legs rtogs nas //
T02TD1268E:34a-20: tshogs gnyis gzhal yas dkyil 'khor gsum //
T02TD1268E:34a-21: zhal gsum g-yas dkar g-yon pa dmar //
T02TD1268E:34a-22: dbus ni sku dang mthun pa nyid //
T02TD1268E:34a-23: rdo rje ral gri g-yas na 'dzin //
T02TD1268E:34a-24: dril bu rtse gsum phyag g-yon na //
T02TD1268E:34a-25: rang ni rang rig yum la 'khyud //
T02TD1268E:34a-26: phyag bzhi rdo rje thod pa dag / g-yas dang g-yon pa'i phyag na 'dzin //
T02TD1268E:34a-27: gnyis ni rig ma nyid la 'khyud //
T02TD1268E:34a-28: phyag gnyis g-yas na rdo rje dang //
T02TD1268E:34a-29: thod pa kha tr'am phyag g-yon na //
T02TD1268E:34a-30: de gsum tshangs pa'i steng na bzhugs //
T02TD1268E:34a-31: gzhan dang sngon du bstan pa nyid //
T02TD1268E:34a-32: spro dang bsdu dang 'khor lo dang //
T02TD1268E:34a-33: de don bsgom dang gtor ma sngags //
T02TD1268E:34a-34: zhal gsum phyag bzhi la sogs rnams //
T02TD1268E:34a-36: rjes thob rnam par dag pa yang //
T02TD1268E:34a-37: dbye ba shes pas rtag tu bsgom //
T02TD1268E:34a-38: me dri dra gur bdud las rgyal //
T02TD1268E:34a-39: rnam thar chos 'byung chos kyi dbyings //
T02TD1268E:34a-40: gshin rje dbugs 'byin dur khrod brgyad //
T02TD1268E:34a-41: sgo bzhi dran pa nye bar gzhag / gru bzhi yang dag song ba bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34a-42: sgo rgyan rdzu 'phrul rkang pa bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34a-43: 'dod yon lha mo dbang po lnga //
T02TD1268E:34a-44: rtsig pa lnga yang stobs lngar dag / rta babs bzhi ni bsam gtan bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34a-45: rten 'brel bcu gnyis dag pas ni //
T02TD1268E:34a-47: rgyan rnams byang chub yan lag bdun //
T02TD1268E:34a-48: ka ba brgyad mdzes 'phags lam brgyad //
T02TD1268E:34a-49: 'khor lo bzhi ni bden pa bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34a-50: de bzhin gdugs ni chad med bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34a-51: byams pa'i thugs ni sku mdog nag / snying rje spyan dmar 'gro la gzigs //
T02TD1268E:34a-52: dpa' bo gar dgu 'gro rnams sgrol //
T02TD1268E:34b-0: @34b btang snyoms sna tshogs rdo rjes mdzes //
T02TD1268E:34b-1: 'khor lo'i gzugs ni mi bskyod pa //
T02TD1268E:34b-2: rna cha dag la 'od dpag med //
T02TD1268E:34b-3: mgul gyi phreng ba rin chen gtso //
T02TD1268E:34b-4: yan lag kun bkod rnam snang mdzad //
T02TD1268E:34b-5: 'od dpag la ni don yod grub //
T02TD1268E:34b-6: yan lag kun thugs rdo rje 'dzin //
T02TD1268E:34b-7: zhal brgyad rnam par thar pa brgyad //
T02TD1268E:34b-8: sku gsum dka' dmar gnag pa'i zhal //
T02TD1268E:34b-9: phyag rnams stong pa bcu drug ste //
T02TD1268E:34b-10: nad rnams 'joms pas glang bo sogs //
T02TD1268E:34b-11: dngos grub myur bas lha mo sogs //
T02TD1268E:34b-12: rus pa'i rgyan yang bden pa bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34b-13: stag gi pags pa byang chub bdun //
T02TD1268E:34b-14: bsdu ba bzhi ni zhabs bzhi yin //
T02TD1268E:34b-15: skye rga bcom pas bdud bzhi mnan //
T02TD1268E:34b-16: bdag med chos sku rnam dag nyid //
T02TD1268E:34b-17: phung po dag pas goo r'i sogs //
T02TD1268E:34b-18: ye shes dag pas kha dog bzhi //
T02TD1268E:34b-19: gri gug sogs kyis bdud bzhi byed //
T02TD1268E:34b-20: tshad ma goms pas khams bzhi la //
T02TD1268E:34b-21: pukka s'i sogs lha mo bzhi / mdog dang phyag mtshan de bzhin no //
T02TD1268E:34b-22: nyin mo bcom ldan thabs su gnas //
T02TD1268E:34b-23: mtshan mo shes rab stong pa nyid //
T02TD1268E:34b-24: 'gro ba'i gar dang phyag rgya bskyod //
T02TD1268E:34b-25: brjod pas thams cad sngags yin no //
T02TD1268E:34b-26: khrus byed dbang bskur bsam gtan dang /
T02TD1268E:34b-27: nyal ba gnyid kyi bsam gtan bsgom //
T02TD1268E:34b-28: de ltar brtan pa'i rnal 'byor pas //
T02TD1268E:34b-29: dbang po mi dgag 'gro rnams bskyab //
T02TD1268E:34b-30: bla ma'i rim 'ongs rgyud rgyal don //
T02TD1268E:34b-31: bsgoms pas blo la gsal ba'i don //
T02TD1268E:34b-32: dgyes rngor mos la phan phyir byas //
T02TD1268E:34b-33: 'di la byung ba'i bsod nams des / bdag dang 'gro ba ma lus pa //
T02TD1268E:34b-34: dgyes rdor myur du 'grub par shog / dpal dgyes pa rdo rje sgrub pa'i thabs /
T02TD1268E:34b-35: rin po che'i sgron ma zhes bya ba /
T02TD1268E:34b-36: slob dpon chen po dpal mar me mdzad ye shes kyis mdzad pa rdzogs so /
T02TD1268E:34b-38: // / rgya gar gyi mkhan po pandi ta d'a na sh'i la dang /
T02TD1268E:34b-39: lo ts'a ba gan dar ma blo gros kyis bsgyur cid [*cing?] zhus so//
